## Summary
This documentation explains data discrepancies between Amplitude analytics platform, Snowflake/Redshift destinations, and Export API, primarily due to timezone differences (Amplitude uses project timezone while Snowflake and Export API use UTC) and query time definitions (Export API uses server_upload_time).

